entry_summary:
Former U.S. men’s national team goalkeeper Tim Howard has called Christian Pulisic’s decision to celebrate a goal using the ‘Trump Dance’ “stupid” and said that he himself would never show support to someone he &#8220;(believes) is racist.&#8221;
Pulisic’s celebration came after he scored the first goal in USMNT’s 4-2 Nations League victory over Jamaica. After the match, the Milan winger was asked about his dance and said he didn’t feel it was a political statement.
“It was just a dance that everyone’s doing,” Pulisic said after confirming it had indeed been the...
